%% Diagram: Flink-style two-phase commit sink lifecycle (begin / preCommit / commit / abort)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant JM as JobManager
    participant Op as Stream operator
    participant Sink as TwoPhaseCommitSink
    participant Ext as External system

    Note over JM,Ext: Phase 0 - new checkpoint epoch
    JM->>Op: inject checkpoint barrier N
    Op->>Sink: process records for epoch N
    Sink->>Ext: beginTransaction for epoch N

    Note over JM,Ext: Phase 1 - PREPARE
    Op->>Sink: snapshotState for epoch N
    Sink->>Ext: flush plus preCommit
    Sink-->>JM: ack barrier and store txnId

    alt all operators ack the barrier
        Note over JM,Ext: Phase 2 - COMMIT
        JM->>Sink: notifyCheckpointComplete
        Sink->>Ext: commit transaction
    else any operator fails to ack
        Note over JM,Ext: Phase 2 - ABORT
        JM->>Sink: checkpoint failed
        Sink->>Ext: abort transaction
    end
